message.body: Damn. That must be so disappointing to be stuck here
Hahah yea. But it won't be too long. Hopefully.
What are your thoughts about having cheesecake for breakfast/my "late night" snack?
Unsurprising for Phuong lol
Thanks?
Considering your schedule I'm not judging is what I meant to say
Sure it is...
No regrets.
Was it delicious? :D
Quite satisfying.
And they're up!
Lol so cute
Aunty, why are you shining bright lights at us?
Because she forgot she left the flash on.
Oopsie daisie...
Did you teach the one on the left how to pose?
No I actually did not! I found it so cute that he was doing that! He was doing it by himself this morning more than once when I was snapping the photos. Oh babies!
He knows how gain and keep your attention. How cute heh
How to*
Funny how you're missing your pancakes. Because IHOP is doing free pancakes today. It's kinda funny to see the line out the door all day in the city with freezing rain and all
Oh nice! Pancakes are awesome!!! I haven't though about pancakes since last night. Tired, too lazy to chew.
I'll chew for you then. Yum
I think that's just straight up stealing my pancakes.
No. I'd deliver it the way birds would.
Ew, no thank you!
Lol chomp chomp
I prefer to have my food masticated on my own.
I know. Just taking the fact that you're lazy to chew out of rational thought lol
How's the day been? It's quite dreary out. Freezing rain =/
I got an hour of sleep in earlier. Yay! But oh would you believe the other stuff that happened today. It's funny yet ahhhh! all at once.
Heh I can't wait to hear about it
Oh it's a whopper.
I want to take a nap and David is asleep but Ethan is wide awake and crawling up a storm!!!
Take care of the crawler then. You can check up on the sleeping one now and then.
But I want to nap too!
Looks appetizing doesn't it?
Oh the memories!
So many tasty mushy flavors lol
We also cooked and blended our own now and then. It was good times
Oh wow, you went all out.
Is that where your interest in cooking piqued?
No. It came from when my palette changed drastically and I obtained a taste for various foods I could enjoy.
http://www.tastenectar.com This is where I had my first service job and taste of fine dining
Good name.
The sushi menu is impressive and I miss having 50% off the menu
Whoa, good for you! Pretty good deal.
What was the baby food you showed me?
A concoction I whipped up with avocado, oatmeal, formula, and peach purée (from jar).
Did you give it a try? I actually like the ingredient list
Of course you would.
And I did not. I like grown up food.
I don't know if you're insulting me or simply stating where you stand on trying food...
Take it as you like it...
You weirdo.
I'm heating up leftovers from home. String beans in garlic soy sauce and fried fish.
Then braving the cold to get some groceries.
Sounds like a tasty dinner.
I thought about your assumption that everyone is dating someone. Does anyone ever assume the same for you?
I don't always assume that.0
They would ask me.
Man, I just passed out col for the last two hours.
Feel good? You're just perpetually sleeping lol
I feel a better than I did two hours ago. At that point I was up for almost 24 hours (with an hour nap tucked in there).
That's fun. Basically how I felt the night we went out
Oh really? Hahah. That was an interesting night.
How was dinner?
Yeah I didn't sleep much that night since we were chatty then I had to drive my srister's to Penn state the next morning
Dinner was pleasant and tasty. I finished with a spoon of green tea ice cream by Hagan Daaz
Oh I didn't even Haagen Dasz made green tea ice cream.
Well now I know how you felt. It's bedtime and they're not sleeping.
And I still need to eat dinner.
Guess it's the time when chewing is necessary hahah.
Yes. No bird feeding =P
Or you could make yourself some baby food hahaha
Eck, I'd rather put in the extra effort to chew and swallow.
That's good. What's for dinner?
Salmon and broccoli.
Oh that's awesome. I love salmon.
I use to really dislike salmon for a while but I've gained a liking and spied custom for it as I've gotten older.
It could be so delicious!
Knock knock.
Maybe it needs to be prepared differently for you?
Why?
Can be cooked different ways to appeal to your tastes. If it's made only one way and you dislike that then you'd never really give it a chance
I guess that's what happened.
Wish I could say good morning but there nite freezing rain lol
